query.query:
query QbtOmnisearch($filters: HcpSocOmnisearchFilters!, $pagination: Pagination!) {
  hcpSocOmnisearch(filters: $filters, pagination: $pagination) {
    countForPagination
    items {
      npi
      socId
      city
      state
      zip
      numUtilizations
      firstname
      lastname
      primaryTaxonomy
      socType
      name
      numBeds
      site_of_care {
        soc_id
        address1
        city
        state
        __typename
      }
      hcp {
        npi
        address1
        city
        state
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}

query.query:
query QbtOmnisearch($filters: HcpSocOmnisearchFilters!, $pagination: Pagination!) {
  hcpSocOmnisearch(filters: $filters, pagination: $pagination) {
    countForPagination
    items {
      npi
      socId
      city
      state
      zip
      numUtilizations
      firstname
      lastname
      primaryTaxonomy
      socType
      name
      numBeds
      site_of_care {
        soc_id
        address1
        city
        state
        __typename
      }
      hcp {
        npi
        address1
        city
        state
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
